Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.26,0:02:06.69,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,It's this condo?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.56,0:02:11.49,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, 9th floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.80,0:02:25.77,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,I'm kinda nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.89,0:02:37.49,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,E-Excuse u-
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.55,0:02:41.06,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,What is all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.06,0:02:42.63,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,It's full of hero figures!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.33,0:02:48.25,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Uncle wrote nothing but hero manga, so he could buy these as business expenses.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.25,0:02:50.22,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,A gag hero manga, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.22,0:02:51.30,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Are you making fun of him?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.30,0:02:52.59,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,I'm respecting him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.70,0:02:55.42,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Take one out and have a look at what's behind it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.52,0:03:01.01,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Ooh, Jack!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.52,0:03:01.01,TL Notes,TL Note,0000,0000,0000,,TL note: "Jack" is a parody of "Jump" the magazine the Bakuman manga is serialized in.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.01,0:03:02.27,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,'96, they sure are old!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.79,0:03:04.27,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm gonna read 'em later.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.27,0:03:07.80,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,It looks like he got all the Jacks from when he was serialized.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.80,0:03:10.90,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Now then, on the other side of this door is the {\i1}real{\i0} workplace.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.84,0:03:20.91,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,What an incredible library of manga volumes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.52,0:03:24.33,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I had a collection, but this is a hundred times the size of it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.64,0:03:27.67,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It sure takes me back.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.54,0:03:30.22,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Just how much did I use to come here?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.60,0:03:33.15,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How much did I talk with Uncle?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.56,0:03:35.50,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,They're in the room over there, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.78,0:03:39.69,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Uncle used to say that the best data for manga {\i1}is{\i0} manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.69,0:03:41.95,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Though with his crappy drawings, maybe he was the only one who said that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.25,0:03:45.36,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, there are raw manuscripts and stuff here too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.36,0:03:46.39,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Could I see them?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.74,0:03:47.57,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.57,0:03:49.30,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm pretty sure they were in that closet.
