Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.09,0:03:57.47,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, is it really okay for me to look at them?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.82,0:03:58.58,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.53,0:04:00.80,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Which one should I pick?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.80,0:04:02.00,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Might as well go with chapter one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.96,0:04:11.51,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first time I've ever seen a raw manuscript.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.92,0:04:14.87,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Manuscripts are fine, but you should take a look at these first.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.54,0:04:16.46,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Names.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.46,0:04:19.53,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Drafts showing where the panels split with rough drawings and the lines put in.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.53,0:04:20.73,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,So {\i1}this{\i0} is a name?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.42,0:04:23.39,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,It's like a rough draft of a manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.39,0:04:26.26,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,I've seen these on the application pages for manga awards.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.24,0:04:35.71,TS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(800,0)\c&H010C08&\3c&HF5FFFC&\b1\fs42\pos(876,207)\bord2.5}Name
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.95,0:04:29.63,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,First, the name is written and it's shown to the editor.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.49,0:04:35.71,TS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(600,0)\c&H010C08&\3c&HF5FFFC&\b1\fs40\bord2.5\pos(874,432)}Editor Check
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.22,0:04:33.31,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Then it's rewritten until he gives the OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.31,0:04:35.73,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Once he gives the OK, you can start making it into a manuscript.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.79,0:04:35.71,TS,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(600,0)\c&H010C08&\3c&HF5FFFC&\b1\fs40\bord2.5\pos(878,654)}Manuscript
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.26,0:04:39.05,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Most people who can just show a name
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.05,0:04:41.05,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,are mangakas whose talent has already been recognized.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.34,0:04:46.30,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,We'll be bringing in a completed manuscript because we need to be recognized first.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.58,0:04:48.52,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I know that much already.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.52,0:04:51.43,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Saikou, do you plan on having me do all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.43,0:04:52.95,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,You mean I can't just write it as text?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.53,0:04:54.85,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.85,0:04:57.63,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of which, you can't just mimic that name either.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.52,0:05:01.05,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Uncle did a gag manga, so the panels were small.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.05,0:05:02.36,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,And it's too simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.99,0:05:05.28,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Write a name that fits your own story.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.83,0:05:06.97,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, didn't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.97,0:05:10.06,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Unless you can write a name I approve of, I won't team up with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.06,0:05:11.39,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, when it comes to the point of doing the art,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.39,0:05:14.75,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll think of the composition and fix the panel splits too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.75,0:05:18.09,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,So Shuujin, please think of a story that would make me want to draw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.25,0:05:22.41,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Saikou... I knew you were great.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.74,0:05:23.41,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.41,0:05:25.04,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do it! I'm gonna do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.04,0:05:27.12,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,I'm kinda fired up about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.12,0:05:29.33,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Saikou, what kind of manga do you wanna draw?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.33,0:05:30.91,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,I like manly manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.53,0:05:33.33,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,A manly manga, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.33,0:05:34.61,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,What kind, specifically?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.33,0:05:36.93,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,What's your favorite manga?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.93,0:05:37.80,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Ashita no Joe!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.89,0:05:41.97,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,With his elbow readied, planted under his left armpit,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.97,0:05:45.75,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,aiming slightly on the inside, like he's boring into him, pow!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.75,0:05:47.49,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,It was a real masterpiece, eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.64,0:05:50.39,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,What's your favourite manga, Shuujin?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.96,0:05:54.10,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Hm, Dragonball I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.68,0:05:58.00,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Just like you said, it's a manga that was written by a genius.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.42,0:05:59.54,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Same with "Joe"...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.30,0:06:02.75,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Whether it's manga or novels,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.75,0:06:05.53,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna read and study everything I can get my hands on.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.01,0:06:09.70,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever the type; battle stories, love stories,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.70,0:06:11.21,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,clear characteristics and rising plot developments...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.21,0:06:13.84,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,are strong things to have, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.30,0:06:18.23,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you really can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.67,0:06:21.64,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Really? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.65,0:06:24.19,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,150)}Uncle once entered to win the Akatsuka Award.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.07,0:06:27.53,Main,Paper,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz353.555\c&H1C2833&\blur14\fscx120\bord0\fnBernard MT Condensed\b0\fs72\fad(100,0)\t(0,800,\blur0)\move(484,116,484,326)}Akatsuka Award
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.48,0:06:27.53,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Of the two big awards, that's the one for gag manga, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.95,0:06:31.74,Main,Paper,0000,0000,0000,,Uncle told me he gathered up all the past winning works...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.74,0:06:34.87,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,675)}and figured out which ones had value and should be studied.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.40,0:06:42.38,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,And he concluded that gag manga with social satire were valued, and it seems it paid off.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.38,0:06:44.52,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,So he won the Atatsuka Award?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.09,0:06:46.42,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,He only got an honorable mention, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.63,0:06:51.13,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,But if you're really going for it, I think that's one strategy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.16,0:06:54.92,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,And you actually just thought of starting with the same kinda thing, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.93,0:06:55.72,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.20,0:06:57.90,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Anyhow, I came all the way here, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.90,0:06:59.85,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna look at as many names as I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.57,0:07:02.50,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,They'll be great for reference.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.50,0:07:04.93,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Especially the places where corrections are marked in red pen.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.93,0:07:06.60,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,I see what they meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.61,0:07:09.95,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm sure Shuujin will be able to think of an interesting story and make it into a name.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.66,0:07:16.29,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I've still never drawn real manga before...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.49,0:07:18.52,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Shuujin?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.52,0:07:20.01,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.01,0:07:23.32,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think we can get an anime version by the time we're 18?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.33,0:07:24.63,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,No, not one bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.42,0:07:27.29,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to be so straightforward about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.29,0:07:31.46,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm pretty sure that, like idols, lots of seiyuus get out there at 18.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.07,0:07:37.34,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Azuki's cute, so... Even before she's earned any real merit,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.34,0:07:39.66,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,she may already have enough to get popular.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.27,0:07:41.48,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Saikou...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.52,0:07:45.77,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,I want to become a mangaka with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.43,0:07:49.75,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,But, right now I feel the same as you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.75,0:07:52.45,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,I really want you and Azuki to be able to get married.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.03,0:07:55.80,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,An anime by 18 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.80,0:07:56.99,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,We'll make that our goal-
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.99,0:07:58.95,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,No, we'll make that our reality!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.16,0:08:01.20,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Shuujin...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.66,0:08:03.83,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,We'll do it! For sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.81,0:08:10.46,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Saikou, is the manuscript this name was made into around somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.09,0:08:13.18,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I'd like to compare them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.18,0:08:15.83,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,It should be in one of the boxes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.83,0:08:17.34,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'm gonna look for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.34,0:08:18.13,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,I'll help.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.43,0:08:20.52,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.78,0:08:27.24,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,But man, there sure are a lot of names.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.24,0:08:29.15,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,And every one of these boxes is packed to the brim.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.03,0:08:33.83,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But to make just one into a manuscript, just how many minutes would it take?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.43,0:08:36.57,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No, how many hours?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.90,0:08:39.84,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}At just what pace did he draw?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.83,0:08:41.91,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}With all these...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.64,0:08:48.64,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to go outside for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.64,0:08:49.35,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Azuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.35,0:08:51.17,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,I told you, I don't know her number.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.69,0:08:55.52,Main,Announcer,0000,0000,0000,,It is now awaiting government action.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.52,0:08:58.70,Main,Announcer,0000,0000,0000,,On to the next new topic, the popular rock singer, KOOGY-san's concert is having its premier...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.70,0:09:02.14,Main,Announcer,0000,0000,0000,,with his female fans first in line, it's quite a happening as the opening time approaches.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.06,0:09:06.39,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.39,0:09:08.90,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,This is the first time you've given me a phone call, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.27,0:09:11.57,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.57,0:09:12.53,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.15,0:09:15.95,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.97,0:09:17.69,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,thought uncle committed suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.70,0:09:21.95,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,He wasn't such a coward.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.95,0:09:25.58,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,He was a man that the more difficult things got, the more he'd bare with it and work hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.46,0:09:28.25,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,And he never once complained about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.00,0:09:30.25,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.24,0:09:35.36,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,He even gave up sleep, and just focused on drawing something.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.64,0:09:40.23,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Moritaka, have you read "Kyojin no Hoshi"?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.23,0:09:41.95,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Eh, yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.95,0:09:44.72,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Then you know Sakamoto Ryouma's line, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.67,0:09:46.67,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.67,0:09:48.60,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,You really liked "Ashita no Joe", right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.77,0:09:51.86,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.86,0:09:54.53,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Dad, you don't need to say any more.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.61,0:09:56.99,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.99,0:09:57.90,Main,Dad,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.95,0:10:02.83,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Sakamoto Ryuuma's words from "Kyojin no Hoshi":
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.74,0:10:07.37,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,225)}"When men die, even if it's in a ditch, die pitching forward."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.69,0:10:12.91,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,And Yabuki Joe, when he was completely worn out, burned away and turned into pure white ash...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.34,0:10:17.88,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Those manga scenes that Dad read to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.32,0:10:21.34,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not going to give it anything less than my all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.34,0:10:23.22,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Manga, Azuki Miho...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.56,0:10:26.35,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,I'll put my life on the line for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.48,0:10:37.72,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,This is interesting, but why was it rejected?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.72,0:10:38.90,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Don't plagiarize.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.99,0:10:41.87,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,I'm don't intend on writing a gag hero manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.12,0:10:45.54,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.58,0:10:51.71,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Letters?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.63,0:10:55.30,TS,Name on Letter,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\frz23.516\fscx85\fnBradley Hand ITC\b1\fs46\pos(928,464)\c&H372344&\blur.8}Haruno Miyuki
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.00,0:10:55.30,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,These are...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.66,0:10:58.41,Main,Kawaguchi,0000,0000,0000,,We went to different high schools,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.42,0:11:00.68,Main,Kawaguchi,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,475)}so we just exchanged letters like those.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.09,0:11:02.72,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,What's up, Saikou?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.72,0:11:04.39,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? Letters?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.39,0:11:08.48,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Uncle told me that he had someone he contacted with ever since his middle school graduation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.48,0:11:09.68,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Contacted with letters?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.68,0:11:10.98,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Man, that's old fashioned.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.00,0:11:12.80,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,So it was a long distance love relationship?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.98,0:11:14.73,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,No, they lived in the same city.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.73,0:11:15.23,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.57,0:11:19.86,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,I kinda feel like we shouldn't look at them.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.86,0:11:21.32,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,O-Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.32,0:11:23.20,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,That would be a violation of privacy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.20,0:11:24.18,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Totally.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.18,0:11:26.18,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Anyhow, get to the name already.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.41,0:11:32.25,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,I, Mashiro Moritaka, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.25,0:11:33.46,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Takagi Akito...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.46,0:11:37.34,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,swear never to tell anyone about the contents of this letter!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.34,0:11:38.00,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,I swear!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.42,0:11:42.72,Main,Miyuki,0000,0000,0000,,"Mashiro-kun, are you doing well?"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.72,0:11:44.93,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,"I'm finally getting used to high school, too."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.43,0:11:50.48,Main,Miyuki,0000,0000,0000,,"To sum up my class, it's like that old youth drama "Tobidase Seishun", was that the name?"
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.10,0:11:53.56,Main,Miyuki,0000,0000,0000,,"I went to an ALFEE concert."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.40,0:11:59.23,Main,Miyuki,0000,0000,0000,,"I hate the rainy season, but I bought two pretty umbrellas, so I've come to like it."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.98,0:12:02.45,Main,Miyuki,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like they only wrote about boring every day stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.45,0:12:06.03,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,I think that even though they both liked each other, they couldn't put it into words.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.03,0:12:07.16,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,I don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.74,0:12:11.04,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Uncle said that he just couldn't confess...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.04,0:12:14.87,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,until he wasn't a gambler anymore, and had become a full-fledged mangaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.87,0:12:17.00,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so that's how it was?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.00,0:12:28.93,TS,Letter,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\b1\fs26\blur1\pos(652,588)\frz20.544\c&H464C4F&\fnFG Charyn}Mashiro Nobuhiro
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.63,0:12:20.09,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,"Congratulations on getting an honorable mention for the Akatsuka Award."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.01,0:12:25.34,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,"I changed residence a little while ago, my address changed so I'll let you know what it is now."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.68,0:12:28.93,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,You can really feel those two taking the steps along their lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.93,0:12:31.60,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Is that the last letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.60,0:12:32.18,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.56,0:12:34.52,TS,Letters,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\b1\fs42\c&H464C4F&\fnFG Charyn\frz18.103\pos(590,447)}Mashiro Nobuhiro
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.56,0:12:34.52,TS,Letters,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\b1\fs42\c&H464C4F&\fnFG Charyn\frz4.363\pos(1153,318)}Mashiro Nobuhiro
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.02,0:12:35.65,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,There's a gap of over a year.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.65,0:12:37.61,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,There hadn't been a letter in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.29,0:12:43.91,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,"I haven't said anything about it up until now, but I'm getting married next Spring."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.49,0:12:50.24,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,What is this? She didn't even once tell him she had a boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.74,0:12:53.21,TS,Center Text,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz12.604\fnFG Charyn\c&H4B4147&\bord0\fs94\move(626,272,624,276)\blur1.2\t($start,$end,\fs102)}married
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.58,0:12:58.54,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wonder how Uncle felt when he read this letter.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.54,0:13:02.51,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,When did "Chou Hero Densetsu" start?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.21,0:13:06.09,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, uh, I'm sure it'll be in the volumes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.39,0:13:10.14,TS,Paper,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnCourier New\bord0\c&H252C2B&\b1\fs36\a7\fscy105\fscx100\pos(1284,564)\frz357.904}Compiled from issues \Nran in Shonen Jack\N 1996 Issue 20 ~ 1996
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.84,0:13:10.14,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Serialized from Spring of 1996, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.18,0:13:13.35,Main,Paper,0000,0000,0000,,The Spring two years after that letter, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.35,0:13:15.39,Main,Paper,0000,0000,0000,,And it wasn't an anime for another two years.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.02,0:13:17.69,Main,Paper,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like he didn't make it in time.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.69,0:13:21.32,Main,Paper,0000,0000,0000,,But it's amazing that even after getting so discouraged, he kept it up until it became an anime.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.19,0:13:25.82,Main,Kawaguchi,0000,0000,0000,,But she was the reason I was able to try so hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.49,0:13:30.70,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.70,0:13:32.24,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Inside the box.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.24,0:13:33.75,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,There's still something in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.67,0:13:39.08,TS,Book,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H419197&\bord0\b1\fnAdobe Garamond Pro Bold\fscx90\frz1.08\fs54\move(644,203,638,230)\t($start,$end,\fs30\fscx85\frz6.53)}Yakusa City Akehi Middle School
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.67,0:13:39.08,TS,Book,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\c&H2B8083&\b1\fnAdobe Garamond Pro Bold\fs114\frz1.643\move(656,554,676,414)\t($start,$end,\fs72\frz7.543)}Graduation Album
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.08,0:13:40.63,TS,Book,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H419197&\bord0\b1\fnAdobe Garamond Pro Bold\fs30\fscx85\frz6.53)\move(638,230,638,232)\t($start,$end,\fs29\frz8.03)}Yakusa City Akehi Middle School
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.08,0:13:40.63,TS,Book,0000,0000,0000,,{\bord0\c&H2B8083&\b1\fnAdobe Garamond Pro Bold\move(676,414,676,404)\fs72\frz7.543\t($start,$end,\fs68\frz9.043)}Graduation Album
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.60,0:13:40.63,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,An album?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.04,0:13:43.52,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Uncle said he couldn't even ask for a photo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.59,0:13:45.26,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Just how pure-hearted was he?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.67,0:13:48.26,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Haruno Miyuki! Look for Haruno Miyuki-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.26,0:13:50.68,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on! Haruno Miyuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.93,0:13:50.68,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,I know, I'm looking!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.19,0:13:58.64,Main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Azuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.27,0:14:00.44,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,It's her mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.44,0:14:02.48,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,This is Azuki's mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.48,0:14:04.86,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,It's DNA! It's totally scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.49,0:14:08.65,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Even the idea of sending each other letters is just like you guys only sending emails to encourage each other!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.65,0:14:10.62,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,It's exactly the same!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.12,0:14:13.16,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,We don't know for sure that it's Azuki's mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.16,0:14:14.58,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,I'm telling you, there's no mistaking it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.58,0:14:15.87,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go confirm it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.87,0:14:16.62,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.00,0:14:20.17,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,We go to Azuki's house again, and we ask her mother directly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.46,0:14:25.30,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow, Tuesday, Azuki has dance classes from 5 to 7.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.30,0:14:26.38,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you know that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.22,0:14:29.22,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Don't underestimate my network of information!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.68,0:14:33.97,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you just ask Azuki what her mom's maiden name is?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.97,0:14:35.66,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Cause I wanna ask about some other stuff, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.43,0:14:37.56,TS,Phone,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz5.019\shad0\fnTahoma\bord0\blur3.6\fs30\pos(843,471)\b0\c&HF3FCFE&\t($start,$end,\blur2)}Receiving call
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.56,0:14:37.68,TS,Phone,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnTahoma\shad0\bord0\blur1.4\fs30\b0\c&HF3FCFE&\pos(735,326)\frz3.761\t($start,$end,\blur.8)}Receiving call
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.56,0:14:37.68,TS,Phone,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnTahoma\shad0\bord0\blur1.6\fs30\b1\c&HF3FCFE&\t($start,$end,\blur0.8)\pos(655,676)\frz3.761}Mashiro Kayoko
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.62,0:14:39.06,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, man. It's my mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.68,0:14:37.81,TS,Phone,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnTahoma\bord0\blur0.6\shad0\fs30\b0\c&HF3FCFE&\frz3.761\pos(653,237)}Receiving call
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.68,0:14:37.81,TS,Phone,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnTahoma\bord0\blur0.6\shad0\fs30\b1\c&HF3FCFE&\frz4.015\pos(596,579)}Mashiro Kayoko
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.81,0:14:37.89,TS,Phone,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnTahoma\bord0\blur0.6\shad0\fs30\b0\c&HF3FCFE&\frz3.761\pos(661,227)}Receiving call
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.81,0:14:37.89,TS,Phone,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnTahoma\bord0\blur0.6\shad0\fs30\b1\c&HF3FCFE&\frz4.302\pos(604,569)}Mashiro Kayoko
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.89,0:14:39.06,TS,Phone,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnTahoma\bord0\blur0.6\shad0\fs30\b0\c&HF3FCFE&\frz3.761\pos(669,217)}Receiving call
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.89,0:14:39.06,TS,Phone,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnTahoma\bord0\blur0.6\shad0\fs30\b1\c&HF3FCFE&\pos(614,561)\frz4.199}Mashiro Kayoko
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.92,0:14:40.84,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.40,0:14:42.20,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,What time do you think it is?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.20,0:14:43.86,Main,Mom,0000,0000,0000,,Come home already!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.70,0:14:59.43,Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,When the test is over I'm going to KOOGY's concert!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.43,0:15:01.74,Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,You got dome tickets? You're so lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.56,0:15:06.41,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,I guess we'll just go to Azuki's house, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.41,0:15:09.89,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so you think those two have some connection too, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.89,0:15:11.42,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,I do not.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.20,0:15:20.52,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.81,0:15:23.60,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, aren't you a little embarrassed sneaking around like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.60,0:15:24.81,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,It's fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.02,0:15:27.28,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel like Giovanni from Death Note!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.78,0:15:32.20,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't have any trouble pushing it today.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.20,0:15:34.24,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,The second time is always easier.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.37,0:15:35.28,Main,Miyuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.74,0:15:37.87,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,It's Miho-san's classmate, Takagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.45,0:15:40.96,Main,Miyuki,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, Miho just stepped out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.96,0:15:43.58,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,No, today we'd like to talk to her mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.58,0:15:44.67,Main,Miyuki,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.67,0:15:47.21,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,It's about the mangaka Kawaguchi Tarou.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.88,0:15:52.93,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This response will tell us if she really was the one who was exchanging the letters...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.47,0:15:57.05,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,We, Mashiro-kun and I, are aiming to become mangakas.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.60,0:16:00.27,Main,Miyuki,0000,0000,0000,,It sure is nice to be young.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.83,0:16:03.07,Main,Miyuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'll serve you some tea, so come on up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.07,0:16:03.90,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.51,0:16:08.26,Main,Miyuki,0000,0000,0000,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.23,0:16:11.53,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Uwah, she really does look like Azuki. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.53,0:16:13.45,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She's a real beauty.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.82,0:16:17.45,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Um, if she was in the same grade as Uncle, she's 42...?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.45,0:16:18.58,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She looks so young!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.58,0:16:21.50,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So Azuki will be like this in 28 years?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.50,0:16:24.40,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But, I think I'll have her give up on the long hair rolls at 42.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.61,0:16:26.26,Main,Miyuki,0000,0000,0000,,What is it, you two?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.26,0:16:27.38,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.38,0:16:28.34,Main,Miyuki,0000,0000,0000,,Come on in, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.71,0:16:32.30,Main,Miyuki,0000,0000,0000,,Sit wherever you want, I'll go get some tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.30,0:16:33.42,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.42,0:16:34.63,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.05,0:16:38.43,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,This is the living room where Azuki spends time in every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.81,0:16:44.89,Main,Miyuki,0000,0000,0000,,Mashiro-kun, you're the son of Mashiro Nobuhiro-kun's brother, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.89,0:16:46.94,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, yes. That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.40,0:16:51.03,Main,Miyuki,0000,0000,0000,,Your father was two years ahead of me in middle school.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.03,0:16:54.11,Main,Miyuki,0000,0000,0000,,He really stood out as captain of the judo team.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.11,0:16:54.78,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.32,0:16:56.91,Main,Miyuki,0000,0000,0000,,Would you two be all right with coffee?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.91,0:16:57.70,Main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.24,0:17:01.54,Main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Mashiro-kun, ah, I mean Mashiro Nobuhiro-kun,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.54,0:17:05.83,Main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,he drank black coffee when he worked hard every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.83,0:17:08.04,Main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,He told me all about it in his letters.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.00,0:17:12.63,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Like I thought, this person really was the recipient of Uncle's letters.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.22,0:17:18.97,Main,Miyuki,0000,0000,0000,,So, ask me anything youngsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.47,0:17:20.64,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.64,0:17:22.06,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, first we have to...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.06,0:17:22.99,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.84,0:17:25.26,Main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,We're sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.56,0:17:28.90,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,We read all of your letters, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.77,0:17:32.07,Main,Miyuki,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no, I'm embarrassed. All of them?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.07,0:17:32.57,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.15,0:17:36.32,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She's blushing, she sure is cute for her age.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.78,0:17:40.07,Main,Miyuki,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I didn't write anything that embarrassing in them, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.07,0:17:40.78,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.78,0:17:42.08,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.08,0:17:45.70,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,They were unbelievably eloquent.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.70,0:17:48.12,Main,Miyuki,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad I didn't write anything too drastic.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.29,0:17:54.63,Main,Miyuki,0000,0000,0000,,So Mashiro-kun kept my letters, did he?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.63,0:17:57.72,Main,Miyuki,0000,0000,0000,,And you two read them?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.09,0:18:00.05,Main,Miyuki,0000,0000,0000,,Well, what's done is done.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.05,0:18:00.68,Main,Miyuki,0000,0000,0000,,I forgive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.89,0:18:02.30,Main,Both,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.01,0:18:06.56,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Um, by saying they were eloquent,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.56,0:18:09.17,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, in a way they were all meandering
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.48,0:18:11.19,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,You really liked him, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.15,0:18:18.03,Main,Miyuki,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.57,0:18:20.91,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,Then why didn't you ever write it in your letters?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.03,0:18:25.41,Main,Miyuki,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't so much that I didn't, but that I couldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.41,0:18:29.54,Main,Miyuki,0000,0000,0000,,It was so embarrassing I didn't feel I could write it down.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.54,0:18:32.79,Main,Miyuki,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I was just waiting for us to tell each other "I like you" together.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.54,0:18:37.55,Main,Miyuki,0000,0000,0000,,But I couldn't wait that long, and I found a new love and got married, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.97,0:18:41.55,Main,Miyuki,0000,0000,0000,,When Miho was 3 years old, I saw on TV...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.64,0:18:52.48,Main,Miyuki,0000,0000,0000,,Kawaguchi Tarou-sensei's manga had become an anime, I was surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.69,0:18:57.69,Main,Miyuki,0000,0000,0000,,I was so happy to know that Mashiro-kun was still working so hard, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.11,0:19:00.57,Main,Miyuki,0000,0000,0000,,I was a bit embarrassed, but,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.57,0:19:03.50,Main,Miyuki,0000,0000,0000,,I went to the convenience store and read "Chou Hero Densetsu".
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.98,0:19:09.68,Main,Miyuki,0000,0000,0000,,And in it a hero named "Otokono Roman" appeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.98,0:19:09.68,TL Notes,Miyuki,0000,0000,0000,,TL note: Otokono Roman is a pun name, meaning "Men's romanticism."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.68,0:19:11.96,Main,TL Note,0000,0000,0000,,When I read that, I think I cried a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.66,0:19:16.67,Main,TL Note,0000,0000,0000,,I understood that Mashiro-kun really did have these kinds of feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.13,0:19:20.32,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Otokono Roman. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.32,0:19:22.15,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}He always worked hard, dreaming of becoming the greatest hero in the universe,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.15,0:19:25.64,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and to confess to a princess he fell in love with at first sight.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.64,0:19:27.70,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,250)}{\i1}He was extremely weak; a failure of a hero.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.28,0:19:32.63,Main,Saikou,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But when he was still weak, the princess approached him herself and confessed.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.52,0:19:33.36,TS,Crown,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz14.72\fnAnime Ace 2.0 BB\bord0\c&H31302E&\fs18\blur1\bord1\3c&HFDFCFA&\pos(270,89)\fad(300,300)}Great
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.25,0:19:37.91,Main,Roman,0000,0000,0000,,Don't come to me yet, wait until I become the greatest hero in the universe!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.91,0:19:40.03,Main,Roman,0000,0000,0000,,Don't just show up out of the blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.31,0:19:48.20,Main,Shuujin,0000,0000,0000,,So that story was a message to you, ma'am?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.20,0:19:50.32,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how I took it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.32,0:19:51.86,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Not bad, that Kawaguchi Tarou.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.72,0:19:56.36,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}So Uncle told his feelings through manga?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.36,0:19:59.28,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Then would it be all right if I asked something?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.28,0:19:59.94,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.69,0:20:02.92,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Takagi-kun, Mashiro-kun,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.92,0:20:05.07,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,which one of you is going out with Miho?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.21,0:20:07.50,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Neither of us yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.50,0:20:09.34,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,But if one of us does in the future, it'll be him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.34,0:20:10.02,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.02,0:20:11.08,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.06,0:20:15.72,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ever since the old days, I've never been into the hard studying type.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.13,0:20:22.24,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Girls tend to like the guys who are kind of the bad boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.07,0:20:24.86,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's just this, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.20,0:20:29.03,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's only your personal preference, but I'm popular with girls too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.03,0:20:30.58,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Also, I have bad eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.58,0:20:31.87,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, sit down.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.75,0:20:34.46,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You're right, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.46,0:20:36.42,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, if you know what I mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.42,0:20:37.96,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think I do at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.34,0:20:43.01,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, there's one thing that's on my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.68,0:20:47.47,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,About how Uncle and you were in the same grade,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.93,0:20:51.89,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,and my uncle being a mangaka, Miho-san doesn't know, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.52,0:20:54.23,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,No, she doesn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.31,0:21:00.27,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd really like it if you wouldn't tell Miho-san those things.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.69,0:21:04.95,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.95,0:21:05.99,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I definitely won't tell her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.70,0:21:08.37,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,You mustn't tell her either, Takagi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.37,0:21:09.58,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.78,0:21:12.87,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Takagi Akito-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.87,0:21:13.95,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.95,0:21:15.83,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Mashiro Moritaka-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.83,0:21:16.75,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.75,0:21:23.63,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Become great mangakas.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.51,0:21:27.01,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be here, rooting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.01,0:21:28.97,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, thank you very much!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.97,0:21:29.64,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.51,0:21:34.39,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,She was a really nice person,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.39,0:21:36.10,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,and an amazing beauty, wasn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.64,0:21:38.65,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I can understand why your uncle fell for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.56,0:21:41.94,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,They were both real romantics, weren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.44,0:21:44.61,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Men's romanticism, huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.94,0:21:45.99,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.99,0:21:48.91,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,We becoming mangakas is a man's romanticism too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.41,0:21:55.45,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, why do you think your uncle's workplace was left like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.59,0:22:07.47,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was in elementary school, my dad and my grandpa both probably knew I admired Uncle.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.26,0:22:11.26,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why neither of them objected.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.89,0:22:13.10,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.10,0:22:14.93,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,They knew this would happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.93,0:22:17.43,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Or rather, they probably hoped.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.94,0:22:20.23,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I sure am blessed.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.23,0:22:21.86,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Not "I", "we"!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.15,0:22:25.36,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what, I will make this dream a reality!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.78,0:22:27.49,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Not "I will", "we will"!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.20,0:22:29.45,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,If I can't do this,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.74,0:22:31.95,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not a man!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.16,0:22:34.28,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.45,0:22:39.54,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Starting tomorrow, no, today, I'm going to start making my drawings into manga artwork!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.54,0:22:42.00,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, and I'll take on making a name!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.80,0:24:20.93,TS,Preview,0000,0000,0000,,{\an3\b1\pos(1062,255)\c&HE6E7E5&}Preview of \NNext Episode
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.39,0:24:18.72,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,I've started running toward the goal of being a mangaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.72,0:24:20.35,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Not "I've", "we've", right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.35,0:24:22.18,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm making a certain decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.18,0:24:23.98,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Not "I'm", "we're," right?
Dialogue: 1,0:24:22.48,0:24:30.50,TS,Preview,0000,0000,0000,,{\an1\b1\pos(241,523)\c&HE6E7E5&}Time\Nand Key
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.98,0:24:25.90,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, Time and Key.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.90,0:24:28.32,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,A dream starts with a choice.
